<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="amused-adj">amused <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'mjuːzd/    美 /ə'mjuːzd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>好玩的；愉快的；开心的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We were all <strong>amused at</strong> / <strong>by</strong> his stories.
我们都被他的故事逗乐了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Playing with water can <strong>keep</strong> children <strong>amused</strong> for hours.
嬉水可以使孩子们玩好几个小时都不烦。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Lucy has a great sense of humour and always keeps her colleagues <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (amuse) with her stories.  （2010 上海改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. amused  </p></div>